headline: PepsiCo, Griffith Foods, and Milh達o Launch Direct Farmer Incentive Pilot Program in Brazil's Cerrado Region to Advance Regenerative Agriculture
summary: PepsiCo (NASDAQ: PEP), in collaboration with Griffith Foods and Milh達o, today announced the launch of a pioneering direct farmer incentive pilot program to advance regenerative agriculture, in Brazil's Cerrado region, one of the world's most biodiverse savannas and a vital agricultural frontier.
